Website:
The official XS-httpd website can be found at http://www.stack.nl/xs-httpd/

Mailing list:
Questions about the use or development of this webserver can be directed
at the mailinglist, <xshttpd-devel@lists.stack.nl>
You can subscribe to this mailinglist via http://lists.stack.nl/
A separate list for announcements about new versions is also available.

Requirements:
XS-httpd 3.6 needs a C compiler that supports C99 language features.

Download sites (anonymous FTP):
ftp.stack.nl:/pub/xs-httpd/
mud.stack.nl:/pub/xs-httpd/

